OL,6,FA drug dealer who was found hiding in
OL,7,Fhis parents' loft after going on the
OL,8,Frun has been jailed.
OL,10,FFaaris Zaman fled the UK after
OL,11,Finvestigators searched his family home
OL,12,Fin and found #89,000 in cash, a vacuum
OL,13,Fpacking machine and handwritten notes
OL,14,Fdetailing deals back to 2018.
OL,16,FZaman, 27, was arrested in July 2020,
OL,17,Finterviewed and released under
OL,18,Finvestigation but then left the
OL,19,Fcountry.
