OL,3,CDrugs boss on the run found hiding in
OL,4,Cparents' loft
OL,6,FHe managed to evade the (NCA) on
OL,7,Freturning to England but was tracked
OL,8,Fto the family address in October 2023.
OL,10,FA three-hour search of the property
OL,11,Fresulted in Zaman being found hiding
OL,12,Fin the loft of the semi-detached home.
OL,14,FAfter his arrest he admitted two
OL,15,Fcounts of conspiracy to supply class A
OL,16,Fdrugs and conspiracy to possess
OL,17,Fcriminal property at Bradford Crown
OL,18,FCourt in March 2024.
