OL,3,CDrugs boss on the run found hiding in
OL,4,Cparents' loft
OL,6,FThe NCA investigation found that Zaman
OL,7,Fhad used the encrypted phone network,
OL,8,FEncroChat, to supply cocaine and
OL,9,Fheroin and handled #1.3 million in
OL,10,Fcriminal profits.
OL,12,FHe had used the handle 'oraclewarrior'
OL,13,Fand was found to have been messaging
OL,14,Fother criminals to deal multiple kilos
OL,15,Fof drugs, moving hundreds of thousands
OL,16,Fof pounds at a time.
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, 22 May, he was sentenced
OL,19,Fto 11 years and seven months in prison.
