OL,6,FNigel Coles, NCA Operations Manager,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Faaris Zaman has suggested he
OL,8,Fplayed a lesser role in this drugs
OL,9,Fsupply network but this was high level
OL,10,Fserious and organised criminality
OL,11,Fwhere his messages showed he was a
OL,12,Fsignificant and trusted operator.
OL,14,F"The messages obtained under Operation
OL,15,FVenetic led us straight to Zaman who
OL,16,Fthought he was operating above law
OL,17,Fenforcement.
